{"tid":374143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AXA傳在港裁250名資訊科技部員工","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T14:55:25.000Z","uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e3d5341c7d219dd266d07001ec97e0bd8dc919","tid":374143,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"外電引述消息報道，法國保險公司AXA安盛在香港裁減約250名資訊科技部（IT）員工，作為削減成本的一部分。 <br />\n<br />\n報道續稱，在重組計劃下，AXA安盛將分別在在馬尼拉及吉隆坡兩處開設資訊科技中心，並擬聘請約400人。 <br />\n<br />\nAXA安盛發言人回覆東網查詢表示，AXA安盛亞洲區恆常檢視業務，以改善產品及提供更佳服務予顧客，並謂該行在亞洲區已建立一個良好的科技系統，以致力提升服務，當中將涉及區內的部分職位調動（rebalancing of some roles in the region）。"},{"pid":"c0088a303558cdbc93bcdef90b73a0653f01f858","tid":374143,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb8b79bee6609732b8a6aee3a2151b35a533bb3","tid":374143,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次國泰果批都唔知吸晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09eb6e2834fe3c399b46f158378d2980fe8a4ff7","tid":374143,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"又係it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862227d2cca3f4e243bf66ddab378844f5818549","tid":374143,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c683220a6c03a108ebcc6216bc219b31d694936","tid":374143,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"炒250 請400<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj